And turning to her selfe his fell intent,
Then turning to those Knights, he gan a new;
They all agreed: so turning all to game,
And turning his feare to faint deuotion,
Then turning to the elder thus he sayd;
And to her turning, thus began againe;
Tho turning all his pride to humblesse meeke,
Then turning vnto him; And you Sir knight
Then turning backe vnto that gentle boy,
Handling and turning them a thousand wayes.
